{"tid":1521780,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[射返你轉頭 !] 水炮車應對方法 ! !","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T13:24:07.000Z","uid":107157,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e964970d6b03949b8db9884199e53dcec4e29821","tid":1521780,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一群人拎住高軔性大水喉整水管 射返你轉頭!</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eTA1Q2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eTA1Q2.jpg&h=85327c8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df21cf5b85c4bbd30becf542a2608d99899d8e01","tid":1521780,"uid":127735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305354aae7ed2829d0062388e54dbd94d44b802c","tid":1521780,"uid":139282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:48:20.000Z","msg":"［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢<br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"fc3a39d05b30fd3d2c2cccbb4e65baf3bfdeba4c","tid":1521780,"uid":231874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84792706c6f029b7d590de224e148b5fb9d3765","tid":1521780,"uid":199893,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:13.000Z","msg":"你都幾on9架喎"},{"pid":"2d89283d5b13e261246659ce48e91afc0938e66b","tid":1521780,"uid":7524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"咪撚推條傻鳩"},{"pid":"12e86b79eb9a3cdbda20ba07333234ce62967d77","tid":1521780,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"邏輯上係得既⋯⋯"},{"pid":"7db483d07189f36f231b0601cf3c855859c8ed6c","tid":1521780,"uid":267983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63f8f25c12490274f5a3d24f2cb7f96702b836e","tid":1521780,"uid":80311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0dfc41d5fbc74aeeb5ce6f168d0dfd4d1e08563","tid":1521780,"uid":279298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:04:50.000Z","msg":"招式難度 SSS"},{"pid":"47ca38321dee0484dfb8de2b9cbdf0cd6069597d","tid":1521780,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59187ee9770ffbcf3a0e591f93c1e0aee980d9b",